.DT
handle_xp
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
handle_xp

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
handle_xp -  This function will give out xp to the player, based on the amount of gps used, the last time the command was used by the player and if the command was successful or not.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs void handle_xp(object person,
int amount,
int success,
string cmd)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^person%^RESET%^ - the player using the command
%^BOLD%^amount%^RESET%^ - the amount of gps used
%^BOLD%^success%^RESET%^ - wether or not the command was successful
%^BOLD%^cmd%^RESET%^ - the name of the command, if this is 0,
previous_object() will be used.

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/xp_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function will give out xp to the player, based on the
amount of gps used, the last time the command was used by
the player and if the command was successful or not.

.EP

